title: Signal Mountain High School vs. Red Bank High School
text: Red Bank, TN (WDEF) - Another rivalry Friday night with Signal Mountain at Red Bank. Eagles trying to get their first win of the year. They go all out on the first play of the game. Corey Dehart deep for Leyton Teal.Ball is overthrown, but Houston, we get a splash-down. Lions on offense testing the airwaves. Caleb Tate to Tra Stamper for the 1st Down, but Stamper doesn't want to go down. Next play, it's the give to Destien Henderson.He goes all the way down to the 19 yard line. Lions are forced to kick a field goal. Sandi Begonavich boots it through. A 34-yarder to make it 3 - 0. Lions keeping the Eagles bottled up. Stamper with the tackle for no gain. Red Bank goes on to win 6 - 3.
